Package: Spower
Title: General Purpose Simulated Power Analysis  
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
   person("Phil", family="Chalmers", email =
                     "rphilip.chalmers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                     comment = c(ORCID="0000-0001-5332-2810"))
Description: Package provides simulation-based methodology for power analysis. Supports Monte Carlo simulation 
   version of a priori power analysis, criterion power analysis, compromise power analysis, and post-hoc
   power analysis. 
Depends:
    SimDesign
